data.description: Own your own Piece of Lake Front Paradise, Imagine watching the Sun Rise from your dock or Florida Room.  Award winning Bass have been caught in this lake.  Brick Custom built home nestled in the woods situated on 2 water front lots with 210 ft. of beautiful King Lake frontage.  What's not to love about this home... Absolutely nothing, one can enjoy fishing for Bass, Brim and Catfish from your very own dock, the doc even has a pole house on it, enjoy camp fires and sweet serenity, no HOA, park your boat or RV in your own yard under a covered Pole Barn with storage for all your fishing equipment, fenced in back yard with plenty of room for pets to run, custom built office with separate entrance and two desk work areas, 4 heavy duty lateral filing cabinets, solid wood custom cabinets throughout. Sunsets and reflections over the lake are amazing. Seller has newer certified raised seal survey.
